      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RISING STAR (6) has been an early market drifter but looks well placed back to benchmark grade here. She's only had two runs in Australia, missing a long neck to the smart Silver Bullet here first up before tackling a stronger race at Caulfield when in the market and not far away. She can peak now and should get every hope. HEY BELLA (5) won two in a row over this route, narrowly beaten here again last start. Neindorf on is a positive while also dropping in weight and she can bounce back to form. PROMISED LAND (4) ran well fresh here over 1400m, getting home late to grab fourth. Up in trip suits much better now. MODOWN (1) hasn't won in a while but his best form reads very well for this and he could turn things around on his favoured deck. GARNACHO (7) next best.",
